Title: Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED) API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the FRED API from the Federal Reserve
    Bank of St. Louis. Covers series observations, metadata, search, categories,
    releases, and bulk fetching. Includes LLM context injection via fred_context().
